To apply this specific 3D Rotating Gradient style across your entire TravelCrew AI platform, you need a prompt that tells the AI to convert this raw CSS into a reusable React component or a global Tailwind configuration.

Global 3D Agentic Button Refactor
ACT AS: Lead Frontend Engineer. TASK: Replace all existing button styles in TravelCrew AI with a high-end, 3D rotating gradient design based on a specific CSS architecture.

TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS:

Base Styling: Set buttons to background: transparent, color: #fff, font-size: 17px, text-transform: uppercase, and font-weight: 600. Apply a border-radius: 10px and perspective: 30rem.

Pseudo-Element Gradient: Use a ::before element for the background.

Colors: linear-gradient(320deg, rgba(0, 140, 255, 0.678), rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.308)).

Transition: Set a 3s transition on the background.

3D Hover Animation: Implement a @keyframes rotate that triggers on hover.

Logic: The ::before element should rotate on the Y-axis from 180deg to 360deg over 1 second.

Shadows: Add a depth-defining shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.308).

IMPLEMENTATION STRATEGY:

Create a reusable AgenticButton component in the /components folder using this logic.

Update the "Find Hotels", "Launch Mission", and "Contact Us" buttons to use this new component.

Ensure the "Midnight Travel" theme remains intact by keeping the deep blue and purple hues consistent with the existing UI.

GOAL: The buttons should feel "engineered"—providing a tactile, 3D response whenever a user interacts with the TravelCrew system.

/* From Uiverse.io by mrhyddenn */ 
button {
  background: transparent;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 17px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600;
  border: none;
  padding: 20px 30px;
  cursor: pointer;
  perspective: 30rem;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.308);
}

button::before {
  content: "";
  display: block;
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: linear-gradient(
    320deg,
    rgba(0, 140, 255, 0.678),
    rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.308)
  );
  z-index: 1;
  transition: background 3s;
}

button:hover::before {
  animation: rotate 1s;
  transition: all 0.5s;
}

@keyframes rotate {
  0% {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }

  100% {
    transform: rotateY(360deg);
  }
}

